description: React functional component 'EmptyState' that displays a placeholder when there is no data in the user dashboard. It includes functionality for admins in development mode to seed sample data via an API call.

methods.name: EmptyState({ onDataSeeded })
methods.description: Functional React component that renders the empty state UI and handles data seeding for admins in development environment.

methods.name: handleSeed
methods.description: Asynchronous function invoked when the seed button is clicked; posts seed request to API and handles success/error states.
